```plantuml
@startuml IBM_datastax-cassandra-clickstream

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Next.js API" as API
participant "clicks.service.js" as ClicksService
participant "DataStax Cassandra" as Database

User -> Frontend: Browse Products
activate Frontend

Frontend -> API: GET /products
activate API

API -> ClicksService: getProducts()
activate ClicksService

ClicksService -> Database: Query Products
activate Database
Database --> ClicksService: Return Products
deactivate Database

ClicksService --> API: Return Products
deactivate ClicksService

API --> Frontend: Return Products
deactivate API

Frontend -> User: Display Products

User -> Frontend: Add to Cart
activate Frontend

Frontend -> API: POST /products/addToCart
activate API

API -> ClicksService: addToCart()
activate ClicksService

ClicksService -> Database: Insert AddToCart Event
activate Database
Database --> ClicksService: Acknowledge Insert
deactivate Database

ClicksService --> API: Acknowledge AddToCart
deactivate ClicksService

API --> Frontend: Acknowledge AddToCart
deactivate API

Frontend -> User: Update Cart UI

User -> Frontend: View Clickstream History
activate Frontend

Frontend -> API: GET /history
activate API

API -> ClicksService: getActivity()
activate ClicksService

ClicksService -> Database: Query Clickstream Data
activate Database
Database --> ClicksService: Return Clickstream Data
deactivate Database

ClicksService --> API: Return Clickstream Data
deactivate ClicksService

API --> Frontend: Return Clickstream Data
deactivate API

Frontend -> User: Display Clickstream History

@enduml
```